<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Lightning_P38_RideXNC.jpg" class="image" title="Lightning P38 (a short wheelbase recumbent) and rider rest during a long tour."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/1/12/Lightning_P38_RideXNC.jpg" width="300" height="231" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
